70
00:08:20.958 --> 00:08:23.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It's about time you showed up.

71
00:08:24.253 --> 00:08:26.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Our mission has changed quite a bit
since the last time I saw you,

72
00:08:26.881 --> 00:08:28.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
but I suppose you're aware of it.

73
00:08:28.633 --> 00:08:30.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I am.

74
00:08:30.593 --> 00:08:33.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
