a few of the blanks for me.

75
00:08:34.222 --> 00:08:37.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The Xindi weapon would be
a good place to start.

76
00:08:37.475 --> 00:08:39.018 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We don't know any more than you do.

77
00:08:39.435 --> 00:08:41.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I thought you and your colleagues

78
00:08:41.771 --> 00:08:44.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
were supposed to be
keeping an eye on the timeline.

79
00:08:44.649 --> 00:08:46.692 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You're from the 30th century.

80
00:08:46.776 --> 00:08:48.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
