about a conflict between humans and Xindi.

82
00:08:52.657 --> 00:08:53.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
How could that be?

83
00:08:53.866 --> 00:08:56.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The events that are taking place
are the result of temporal incursions.

84
00:08:56.744 --> 00:08:58.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
They are not supposed to be happening.

85
00:08:58.371 --> 00:09:00.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-But they are happening.
-Yes, they are.

86
00:09:00.373 --> 00:09:02.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But the outcome hasn't reached us yet.

87
00:09:02.833 --> 00:09:05.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It takes a while for changes
to ripple through the timeline.

88
00:09:05.503 --> 00:09:08.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The time traveler...
the man the Suliban work for...

89
00:09:08.923 --> 00:09:10.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What about him?

90
00:09:10.716 --> 00:09:13.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He's the one who told us
about the weapon being built.

91
00:09:14.053 --> 00:09:16.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Should I believe him?
-You have no reason not to.

92
00:09:16.847 --> 00:09:20.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You said I'm supposed to play
some crucial part in history.

93
00:09:20.518 --> 00:09:22.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Does this have something to do with it?

94
00:09:22.395 --> 00:09:24.605 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I wish I could say that it does,
but I don't know.

95
00:09:24.689 --> 00:09:27.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I told you,
none of this was supposed to happen.

96
00:09:27.525 --> 00:09:29.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You're not being very helpful!

97
00:09:32.655 --> 00:09:34.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Why are you here?

98
00:09:34.615 --> 00:09:37.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We've detected three Xindi
where they're not supposed to be.

99
00:09:37.577 --> 00:09:40.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
This expanse is filled with Xindi.

100
00:09:40.204 --> 00:09:42.081 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'm not talking about the expanse.

101
00:09:42.164 --> 00:09:44.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'm talking about Detroit, Michigan.

102
00:09:44.417 --> 00:09:46.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
150 years ago.

103
00:09:47.253 --> 00:09:48.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( door chimes )

104
00:09:54.885 --> 00:09:56.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( door chimes )

105
00:09:59.849 --> 00:10:02.059 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Sorry to get you up,
but this couldn't wait.

106
00:10:02.143 --> 00:10:03.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Come in.

107
00:10:12.612 --> 00:10:15.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I just had a visit from Daniels.

108
00:10:17.617 --> 00:10:21.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I think all your doubts about time travel
are about to go out the window.

109
00:10:21.996 --> 00:10:23.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Meaning?

110
00:10:24.040 --> 00:10:29.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Daniels and his team
have discovered three reptilians on Earth.

111
00:10:29.128 --> 00:10:31.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
In the early 21st century.

112
00:10:31.672 --> 00:10:34.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He wants to send us back
to find out what they're doing.

113
00:10:35.009 --> 00:10:36.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Us?

114
00:10:36.135 --> 00:10:38.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He told me I could bring one person,
no more.

115
00:10:39.138 --> 00:10:41.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
If Daniels is the time traveler
he claims to be,

116
00:10:41.849 --> 00:10:43.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
why doesn't he find out for himself?

117
00:10:45.061 --> 00:10:47.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It took him a long while
to get permission to interact with me.

118
00:10:48.064 --> 00:10:49.690 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
There are clearances.

119
00:10:49.774 --> 00:10:51.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
He said it would take too much time.

120
00:10:52.318 --> 00:10:55.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I would think he would have
all the time in the world.

121
00:10:55.321 --> 00:10:59.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He said the three Xindi traveled
to Earth from our century.

122
00:10:59.825 --> 00:11:01.786 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
They've been there for two months.

123
00:11:03.746 --> 00:11:06.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
They're not sightseeing, T'Pol.

124
00:11:06.207 --> 00:11:08.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We have to find out what they're up to.

125
00:11:08.501 --> 00:11:10.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
How are we supposed to accomplish this?

126
00:11:11.003 --> 00:11:13.672 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He wants us to meet him in
the command center at 0800 tomorrow.

127
00:11:18.594 --> 00:11:19.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Come on, boy.

128
00:11:21.305 --> 00:11:23.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Check the database.

129
00:11:23.265 --> 00:11:25.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
