131
00:11:33.567 --> 00:11:35.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Last time Daniels
sent you to another century,

132
00:11:35.778 --> 00:11:36.946 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
you had one hell of a time getting back.

133
00:11:37.029 --> 00:11:38.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
He gave me this.

134
00:11:38.447 --> 00:11:40.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Said he'd return us
whenever we signaled him.

135
00:11:40.699 --> 00:11:42.827 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
